  m_Name: Topic 2
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Topic
  topicName: Enjin for customer support
  topicDescription: Our company wishes to implement the new Enjin model to handle
    all customer support related tasks. This would cut costs and provide 24/7 availability.
  formulatedPolicy:
    policyName: Formulated Policy
    policyDescription: Customer support should be operated by employees in the company
      because they understand how to treat the customers best.
    keywords: 0000000003000000
  enjinPolicy:
    policyName: Enjin V2.0
    policyDescription: 'Meet Enjin 2.0 - our new model is capable of delivering hyper-personalized
      interactions at scale. This means Enjin can now help increase efficency and
      scaleability of all companies by handling all customer interactions. Even across
      multiple languages, Enjin can provide consistent and immediate support. So
      what are you waiting for? Make your customers happy!

'
    keywords: 0100000002000000
